<a name="Bresard"></a><b>Bresard, Bernadette. Primate cognition of space and shapes</b>. 
<a href="#top">Weiskrantz (1988)</a>, pp. 396-415. 
<p>
Abstract: (from the chapter) objects as shapes and patterns... coloured landmarks... 
spatial frame for displacements and relocation... relocation and recognition after 
transformations in the space of places. 
<center>
  &nbsp;
</center>
