  |&nbsp; <a href="../CogSci/index.html">CogSci index</a>&nbsp; |&nbsp; <a href="../index.html">CogWeb</a>
</center>
<center>
  &nbsp;
</center>
<a name="Gazzaniga"></a><b>Gazzaniga, Michael S. The dynamics of cerebral specialization 
and modular interactions</b>. <a href="#top">Weiskrantz (1988)</a>, pp. 430-450. 
<p>
Abstract: (from the chapter) pre- and post-operative evaluation of commissurotomy 
patients... post-operative variability for cognitive tasks... the 'what' of lateral 
specialization... right hemisphere capacities: windows on modularity. 
<center>
  &nbsp;
</center>
